# Feeef Dart SDK (this package)

- **Consumers**: **`feeefapps/marchant`** and potentially other Flutter apps; published/consumed as **`feeef`** (e.g. git `feeefapp/feeef_sdk`).
- **API**: Implemented by **`feeefapps/backend`**. Keep request/response models and repos aligned with backend controllers.
- **When changing public API** of this SDK: bump version/changelog; merchant app may need dependency update. JS storefront uses npm **feeef** — not this package; duplicate shape drift is a risk — document cross-stack fields.

Run tests after repository or model changes.
